---
import Feature from 'components/Feature';
import DefaultLayout from 'layouts/DefaultLayout.astro';

export const prerender = true;
---
<DefaultLayout title="Team">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="mb-8">Meet the Team</h1>
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-stretch gap-8 mb-10">
      <img width="750" height="403" class="rounded-lg md:w-2/3 max-w-lg w-full m-auto" alt="Our robotics team" src="/team.jpeg" />
      <Feature title="The Team" className="md:w-1/3">
        <p>
          Our team works tirelessly, given just six weeks to design, build, and program a robot to bring to competition.
        </p><br>
        <b>Team Manager: Natalie Stopf</b><br>
        <b>Assistant Team Manager: Kristen Sheehan</b><br>
      </Feature>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col-reverse items-stretch md:grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-10">
      <Feature title="Build Team">
        <p>
          This is Bob The Builder's department. We work tirelessly throughout the season to build the most competitive robot possible.
        </p><br>
        <b>Captain: Eoin O&apos;Hern</b><br>
      </Feature>
      <img width="1280" height="1280" alt="The build team" src="/teams/build.png" class="rounded-lg m-auto max-w-lg w-full" />
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col items-stretch md:grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-10">
      <img width="894" height="1280" alt="The programming team" src="/teams/programming.png" class="rounded-lg m-auto max-w-lg w-full" />
      <Feature title="Programming">
        <p>
          The Programming Team's main purpose is to code the robots used in the competitions. Without their help, our robots would be motionless!
          <br><br>
          Our Lieutenant Captain offers programming lessons every thursday so newer members can learn the fundamentals of robotics programming.
          This includes advanced programming concepts such as motion profiling, PID, feedforward tuning, vision processing (both 2D and 3D), and more!
          Our programming team is also responsible for building the website you are viewing right now! 
        </p><br>
        <!--
        Shoutout Fern and Micheal fr -Ian 
        -->
        <b>Captain: Spencer McCurry</b><br>
        <b>Lieutenant Captain: Adam Shafer</b><br>
      </Feature>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col-reverse items-stretch md:grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-10">
      <Feature title="Safety">
        <p>
          Safety is responsible for makign sure everything&apos;s working properly and preventing any injuries during the building process.
        </p><br>
        <b>Captain: Areen Amr</b><br>
        <b>Lieutentant Captain: Noah Sorenson</b>
      </Feature>
      <img width="1280" height="1011" alt="The safety team" src="/teams/safety.jpeg" class="rounded-lg m-auto max-w-lg w-full" />
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col items-stretch md:grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-10">
      <img width="1280" height="1280" alt="The PR team" src="/teams/pr.png" class="rounded-lg m-auto" />
      <Feature title="PR">
        <p>
          The Public Relations team is devoted to getting the ARGS Robotics name known through the use of social media
          (MySpace, HotMail emailing list, etc) and other forms of communication.
        </p><br>
        <b>Captain: Denilson Leveron</b><br>
        <b>Lieutentant Captain: Harper Percival</b><br>
      </Feature>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col-reverse items-stretch md:grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-10">
      <Feature title="Business">
        <p>Let&apos;s get down to business.</p><br>
        <b>Captain: Jonah Collazo-Heifetz</b><br>
        <b>Lieutenant Captain: Ethan Percival</b>
      </Feature>
      <img width="1280" height="1280" alt="The business team" src="/teams/business.png" class="rounded-lg m-auto max-w-lg w-full" />
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col items-stretch md:grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-10">
      <img width="1280" height="1280" alt="The scouting team" src="/teams/scouting.png" class="rounded-lg m-auto max-w-lg w-full" />
      <Feature title="Scouting">
        <p>The Scouting team&apos;s purpose is to monitor the competition and ensure a competitive season.</p><br>
        <b>Captain: Joel East Jr.</b><br>
        <b> Lieutenant Captain: Ethan Bolte</b>
      </Feature>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col-reverse items-stretch md:grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-10">
      <Feature title="Business">
        <p>Let&apos;s get down to business.</p><br>
        <b>Captain: Kai Gray</b><br>
        <b>Liutenant Captain: Troy Kroek</b>
      </Feature>
      <img width="1280" height="1280" alt="The CAD team" src="/teams/cad.png" class="rounded-lg m-auto max-w-lg w-full" />
    </div>
</DefaultLayout>